--- Switchblade ---

Switchblade smiles as he watches the monitors. The Dark Avian was nearing futur Florida. "Not long now," He mumbles to himself as his green visor slides over his eyes. What Firestrike now sees appears in front of him. "Firestrike, keep Megatron alive. Though i suspect that you were already trying to do that before i even connected to you. Look around, I need to see what is happening." Switchblade waits impatiently.
